*2011-09-02:
	ebuild update to get rid of use of kernel_is in the main ebuild core

*2011-08-24:
	minor edit the ebuild header and major edit to the ChangeLog

*2011-08-16:
	merged aufs{,2}-util-9999.ebuild to make it file collisions more manageable
	and pkg block more easier.

*2011-08-15:
	+aufs-standalone-9999.ebuild for kernel >=3.0.

*2011-08-10:
	added header USE flag to make it possible to build the utiliy against 
	a kernel or aufs2-standalone external module.

*2011-08-08:
	+aufs2-standalone-9999.ebuild
